    <url>/2026/05/03/ESP32-S3_%E9%9F%B3%E9%A2%91I2C%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E4%BB%AA%E6%B5%8B%E9%87%8F/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-输出电平测试"><a href="#1-输出电平测试" class="headerlink" title="1. 输出电平测试"></a>1. 输出电平测试</h2><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">setup</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  Serial.begin(<span class="number">115200</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  pinMode(I2C_SCL, OUTPUT);</span><br><span class="line">  pinMode(I2C_SDA, OUTPUT);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> val = <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">loop</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  digitalWrite(I2C_SCL, val);</span><br><span class="line">  digitalWrite(I2C_SDA, <span class="number">1</span> - val);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  delay(<span class="number">1000</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  val = <span class="number">1</span> - val;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>如下，示波器上均匀输出两个通道相反的波形，测试OK，引脚正常。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Fx-i/PictureBed@main/img/20260503152825676.png" alt="image-20260503152825629"></p>
<h2 id="2-I2C链路正常测试"><a href="#2-I2C链路正常测试" class="headerlink" title="2. I2C链路正常测试"></a>2. I2C链路正常测试</h2><h3 id="2-1-原理图上拉电阻确认"><a href="#2-1-原理图上拉电阻确认" class="headerlink" title="2.1 原理图上拉电阻确认"></a>2.1 原理图上拉电阻确认</h3><p>应该要先去看音频模块的原理图，是否加了上拉电阻<br>以我买的ES8311 + NS4150B为例，就没有原理图，<span style="font-size: 18px; color: red">此时要去测SCL&#x2F;SAL的电压值</span></p>
<p>I2C的原理(开漏)<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Fx-i/PictureBed@main/img/20260503152151201.png"><br>I2C 协议规范要求 SDA 和 SCL 两条线路上必须有上拉电阻。这是因为 I2C 总线采用开漏（Open-Drain)电路结构，设备只能将信号线拉到低电平，而不能主动输出高电平。上拉电阻的作用就是在总线空闲时，将信号线拉回到高电平，确保通信正常。</p>
<p>使用万用表去测量电压，毕竟没有上拉电阻，总线上应该不会有正常的高电平<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Fx-i/PictureBed@main/img/20260503152201758.png" alt="image-20260503152201708"></p>
<h3 id="2-2-逻辑分析仪测量写出数据"><a href="#2-2-逻辑分析仪测量写出数据" class="headerlink" title="2.2 逻辑分析仪测量写出数据"></a>2.2 逻辑分析仪测量写出数据</h3><p>I2C测试代码，主要分为三部分</p>
<ol>
<li>设备扫描</li>
<li>数据写入</li>
<li>数据写入再读出</li>
</ol>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&quot;Arduino.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&quot;es8311.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&quot;Wire.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ES8311 es;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> I2C_SCL 4</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> I2C_SDA 5</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;Wire.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> ES8311_ADDRESS   0x18    <span class="comment">// ES8311默认I2C地址（部分模块是0x11）</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> TEST_REG_ADDR 0x00    <span class="comment">// ES8311测试用寄存器（芯片ID寄存器）</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title function_">i2c_write_byte</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">uint8_t</span> dev_addr, <span class="type">uint8_t</span> reg_addr, <span class="type">uint8_t</span> data)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  Wire.beginTransmission(dev_addr);        <span class="comment">// 启动I2C传输</span></span><br><span class="line">  Wire.write(reg_addr);                   <span class="comment">// 发送寄存器地址</span></span><br><span class="line">  Wire.write(data);                       <span class="comment">// 发送要写入的数据</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="type">uint8_t</span> err = Wire.endTransmission();   <span class="comment">// 结束传输，返回错误码</span></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> (err == <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    Serial.<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;I2C Write Success:Dev 0x%02X → Reg 0x%02X → Data 0x%02X\n&quot;</span>, dev_addr, reg_addr, data);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    Serial.<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;I2C Write Failed:ErrorCode%d → Dev 0x%02X Reg 0x%02X\n&quot;</span>, err, dev_addr, reg_addr);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 3. I2C读取函数（验证写入是否生效）</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">uint8_t</span> <span class="title function_">i2c_read_byte</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">uint8_t</span> dev_addr, <span class="type">uint8_t</span> reg_addr)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  Wire.beginTransmission(dev_addr);</span><br><span class="line">  Wire.write(reg_addr);                   <span class="comment">// 发送要读取的寄存器地址</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="type">uint8_t</span> err = Wire.endTransmission(<span class="literal">false</span>); <span class="comment">// 不释放总线</span></span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> (err != <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    Serial.<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;I2C Read Address Failed:ErrorCode %d → DevAddr 0x%02X Reg 0x%02X\n&quot;</span>, err, dev_addr, reg_addr);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0xFF</span>; <span class="comment">// 返回无效值</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  Wire.requestFrom(dev_addr, <span class="number">1</span>);          <span class="comment">// 请求读取1个字节</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> (Wire.available()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">uint8_t</span> data = Wire.read();</span><br><span class="line">    Serial.<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;I2C Read Success: Dev 0x%02X → Reg 0x%02X → Data 0x%02X\n&quot;</span>, dev_addr, reg_addr, data);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> data;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    Serial.println(<span class="string">&quot;I2C Read Empty&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0xFF</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">setup</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  Serial.begin(<span class="number">115200</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  delay(<span class="number">200</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 初始化I2C总线</span></span><br><span class="line">  Wire.begin(I2C_SDA, I2C_SCL);</span><br><span class="line">  Wire.setClock(<span class="number">400000</span>); <span class="comment">// 400kHz（ES8311支持）</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 第一步：先扫描设备，确认通信通路</span></span><br><span class="line">  Serial.println(<span class="string">&quot;Step1: Scan I2C Device&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  Wire.beginTransmission(ES8311_ADDRESS);</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> (Wire.endTransmission() == <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    Serial.<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;find I2C Device:0x%02X(ES8311)\n\n&quot;</span>, ES8311_ADDRESS);</span><br><span class="line">  &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    Serial.<span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Can&#x27;t find I2C Device:0x%02X\n&quot;</span>, ES8311_ADDRESS);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span>; <span class="comment">// 通信不通，直接退出</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 第二步：写入测试数据到寄存器</span></span><br><span class="line">  Serial.println(<span class="string">&quot;Step2: Write Data&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="type">uint8_t</span> write_data = <span class="number">0x12</span>; </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="type">bool</span> write_ok = i2c_write_byte(ES8311_ADDRESS, TEST_REG_ADDR, write_data);</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 第三步：回读寄存器，验证写入是否生效</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">if</span> (write_ok) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    Serial.println(<span class="string">&quot;Step3: Write Then Read Data&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">uint8_t</span> read_data = i2c_read_byte(ES8311_ADDRESS, TEST_REG_ADDR);</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (read_data == write_data) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      Serial.println(<span class="string">&quot;Test OK&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      Serial.println(<span class="string">&quot;Write Data != Read Data&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">loop</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  delay(<span class="number">1000</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="逻辑分析仪配置I2C解析器"><a href="#逻辑分析仪配置I2C解析器" class="headerlink" title="逻辑分析仪配置I2C解析器"></a><span style="font-size: 20px; color: orange">逻辑分析仪配置I2C解析器</span></h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Fx-i/PictureBed@main/img/20260503152214170.png" alt="image-20260503152214135"></p>
<h4 id="I2C数据解析"><a href="#I2C数据解析" class="headerlink" title="I2C数据解析"></a><span style="font-size: 20px; color: orange">I2C数据解析</span></h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Fx-i/PictureBed@main/img/20260503152222786.png" alt="image-20260503152222729"><br>一共三个波形，对应三个测试</p>
<h5 id="I2C设备扫描"><a href="#I2C设备扫描" class="headerlink" title="I2C设备扫描"></a>I2C设备扫描</h5><p>Master发送7位的地址到总线上，对应的设备回应一个ACK</p>
<p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Fx-i/PictureBed@main/img/20260503152230357.png" alt="image-20260503152230325"></p>
<h5 id="I2C数据写入"><a href="#I2C数据写入" class="headerlink" title="I2C数据写入"></a>I2C数据写入</h5><p>先后发送写入的设备地址，写入的Reg地址，以及写入的数据<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Fx-i/PictureBed@main/img/20260503152240333.png" alt="image-20260503152240287"></p>
<h5 id="I2C数据读出验证"><a href="#I2C数据读出验证" class="headerlink" title="I2C数据读出验证"></a>I2C数据读出验证</h5><ol>
<li>Master 发送写指令：取地址为 0x18设备的 0x00寄存器<br> Slave先要获取到具体的地址</li>
<li>Master 再发送读指令</li>
<li>Slave 回应给Master数据<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Fx-i/PictureBed@main/img/20260503152251430.png" alt="image-20260503152251382"></li>
</ol>
<h4 id="I2C地址解析"><a href="#I2C地址解析" class="headerlink" title="I2C地址解析"></a>I2C地址解析</h4><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Fx-i/PictureBed@main/img/20260503152258084.png" alt="image-20260503152258043"><br>一般CE为0，也就是ES8311的地址一般为0x18</p>
<p>和es8311.cpp 也能够对的上</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> ES8311_ADDR              0x18</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<h2 id="3-通过I2C配置ES8311"><a href="#3-通过I2C配置ES8311" class="headerlink" title="3. 通过I2C配置ES8311"></a>3. 通过I2C配置ES8311</h2><p>主要参考开源<br><a href="https://github.com/schreibfaul1/ESP32-audioI2S/tree/master/examples">https://github.com/schreibfaul1/ESP32-audioI2S/tree/master/examples</a><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Fx-i/PictureBed@main/img/20260503152311401.png" alt="image-20260503152311343"><br>此时设置波形有一堆的I2C写入写出，通信是正常的。I2C的调试到这里应该也就OK了。<br>实现代码如下</p>
<figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&quot;Arduino.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&quot;es8311.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&quot;Wire.h&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> I2C_SCL 4</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> I2C_SDA 5</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ES8311 es;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">setup</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    Serial.begin(<span class="number">115200</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(!es.begin(I2C_SDA, I2C_SCL, <span class="number">400000</span>)) </span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">      Serial.println(<span class="string">&quot;ES8311 I2C Init Failed&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    Serial.println(<span class="string">&quot;ES8311 I2C Init Success&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    es.setVolume(<span class="number">50</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    es.setBitsPerSample(<span class="number">16</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">loop</span><span class="params">()</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  delay(<span class="number">1000</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
